ZH: 考虑到天气可能会变冷，我建议你穿厚一点的衣服。
EN: Considering that the weather might get colder, I suggest you wear something thicker.

ZH: 考虑到时间有限，我们必须加快工作的进度。
EN: Considering that time is limited, we must accelerate the progress of our work.

ZH: 考虑到大家的需要，我们决定增加更多的公共交通工具。
EN: Considering everyone's needs, we have decided to increase the number of public transportation.

ZH: 考虑到他的能力，我们委任他担任项目的领导人。
EN: Considering his abilities, we appointed him as the project leader.

ZH: 考虑到疫情的影响，我们推迟了会议的日期。
EN: Considering the impact of the pandemic, we postponed the date of the meeting.

ZH: 考虑到经济的不稳定，我们决定暂时减少开支。
EN: Considering the economic instability, we decided to temporarily reduce expenses.

ZH: 考虑到他的经验和专业知识，我们请他加入我们的团队。
EN: Considering his experience and expertise, we invited him to join our team.

ZH: 考虑到学生的反馈意见，我们对教学内容做出了调整。
EN: Considering the feedback from students, we made adjustments to the teaching material.

ZH: 考虑到市场需求，我们发展了新的产品线。
EN: Considering the market demand, we developed a new product line.

ZH: 考虑到健康因素，我打算开始锻炼身体。
EN: Considering health factors, I plan to start exercising.

ZH: 考虑到家人的意见，我决定放弃这个工作机会。
EN: Considering my family's opinions, I have decided to give up this job opportunity.

ZH: 考虑到他的困难，我愿意帮助他解决问题。
EN: Considering his difficulties, I am willing to help him solve the problems.

ZH: 考虑到安全原因，我们建议您不要晚上单独外出。
EN: Considering safety reasons, we suggest you avoid going out alone at night.

ZH: 考虑到未来的发展，我们正在寻找新的合作伙伴。
EN: Considering future development, we are searching for new partners.

ZH: 考虑到经济形势，公司决定暂时冻结员工的薪水。
EN: Considering the economic situation, the company has decided to temporarily freeze employees' salaries.

ZH: 考虑到客户的需求，我们提供了更多定制化的产品选择。
EN: Considering customers' needs, we offer more customized product options.

ZH: 考虑到环境保护，我们采用了更环保的生产工艺。
EN: Considering environmental protection, we have adopted more eco-friendly production processes.

ZH: 考虑到工作压力，我计划去度假放松一下。
EN: Considering work pressure, I plan to take a vacation to relax.

ZH: 考虑到专业要求，我们要求申请者具备相关工作经验。
EN: Considering professional requirements, we require applicants to have relevant work experience.

ZH: 考虑到市场竞争，我们需要提升产品的品质和性能。
